think, increase the feeling

00:05:41.370 --> 00:05:44.060
that users have of a responsive
browser and a

00:05:44.060 --> 00:05:46.700
responsive website.

00:05:46.700 --> 00:05:48.820
So that's one.

00:05:48.820 --> 00:05:53.900
